1.10	Fast-penta	Vorkosigan Saga	The Vorkosigan Saga is a series of science fiction novels and short stories set in a common fictional universe by American author Lois McMaster Bujold. Most of these were published between 1986 and 2002, with the exceptions being “Winterfair Gifts” (2004) and Cryoburn (2010). Works in the series have received numerous awards and nominations, including winning four Hugo awards.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/70/Wormhole_travel_as_envisioned_by_Les_Bossinas_for_NASA.jpg/220px-Wormhole_travel_as_envisioned_by_Les_Bossinas_for_NASA.jpg
